HIKARU: Akari's been taking
Go classes all summer.

280
00:22:27,410 --> 00:22:30,148
SAI: She's become quite
a talented player.

281
00:22:30,148 --> 00:22:31,733
HIKARU: Yeah, maybe

282
00:22:31,767 --> 00:22:33,535
SAI: And everyone will
be surprised to see

283
00:22:33,568 --> 00:22:35,637
how much you've
improved, Hikaru.

284
00:22:35,670 --> 00:22:37,839
HIKARU: I could be the best
player in the Go club now.

285
00:22:37,873 --> 00:22:41,576
SAI: Yuuki and Kimihiro
may not agree with you.

286
00:22:41,576 --> 00:22:44,780
Next time, Hikaru's
True Strength.

287
00:22:44,813 --> 00:22:49,184
HIKARU: Then I'm gonna challenge
them and show them who's best.

